Package it.unibo.csr.big.cubeload.schema

Class SelectionPredicate

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibo.csr.big.cubeload.schema.SelectionPredicate
  • public class SelectionPredicate
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements a fundamental component of an OLAP query: the selection predicate. A selection predicate is based on a hierarchy level and constrains it to a single value; it may be a segregation predicate, an year prompt or a normal predicate.

        hierarchy - The selection predicate's signature hierarchy.

        element - An element taken from the level's distinct values.
        yearPrompt - A flag, set if the predicate is an year prompt.
